title: Legacy - Radio Drama
description:
2 x 45 mins

Brother and sister team Dan and Rachel are Probate investigators, attempting to trace heirs for the unclaimed estates of the deceased. In these two plays however, they bite off more than they can chew.

1) Eden - Tracking the heirs leads the couple to Kenya, where they discover long hidden secrets going back to the Mau Mau rebellion of the 1950s.

2) Suspicious Minds - In seeking the heirs of Petra Oster, they discover that Petra fled to London from East Germany in the 1980s and there are many mysteries in her life.
